# Project Summary

The Olist E-Commerce Analytics Suite is an end-to-end Business Intelligence project developed using the Brazilian Olist Marketplace dataset. The project demonstrates the complete analytics workflow, beginning with raw data preparation and ending with an interactive Power BI dashboard that supports business decision-making.

The project combines Microsoft Excel, SQL, Power Query, DAX, and Power BI to transform raw transactional data into meaningful business insights.

