# Key Business Insights

* Revenue shows strong seasonal growth during November.
* Health & Beauty is the highest revenue-generating category.
* Bed Bath & Table records the highest product sales volume.
* Credit Card is the most frequently used payment method.
* Order fulfillment exceeds 97%.
* Customer ratings decrease as delivery delays increase.
* Delivery performance differs across states, highlighting opportunities for logistics optimization.

